news.description: Sead Kolasinac is a perfect fit for Arsenal, Bundesliga expert Olly Knaack has told talkSPORT 2. The Gunners are said to have signed the Bosnia and Herzegovina left-back on a free transfer, with the deal going through on July 1. A number of clubs have been linked with Kolasinac, 23, due to his expiring contract and his excellent run of form for Schalke this season.
